final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.
final_hyps.brown: Brown objects are False Walls. The agent can move through False Walls.
final_hyps.yellow: The yellow object is a Key. The agent can pick up the Key by moving into its space. While holding the Key, the agent is colored purple.
final_hyps.cyan: The cyan object is a KeyDoor. When the agent moves onto this object, the KeyDoor opens and the Key is destroyed. The agent cannot move through the KeyDoor while it is closed.

solve_plan: First determine that the green object is the Goal object. Align the agent on the horizontal axis (y=8) since it is already aligned. Next, move to pick up the yellow Key by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=5, it must move RIGHT 13 - 5 = 8 times. Then, while holding the Key, move to reach the cyan KeyDoor by moving RIGHT. Because the agent is at x=13, it must move RIGHT 18 - 13 = 5 times. Once on the KeyDoor, it will open and the Key will be destroyed. Finally, move DOWN to align with the green Goal object, which is one space below, so move DOWN 1 time. Then, move RIGHT to reach the goal (x=19) by moving RIGHT 1 time.
